Design Overview : Main -> MainWindow -> VideoProcessing -> ( Preprocess, FeatureExtraction, Display )

Class Details : 
MainWindow : Handle video file loading and other menu options

VideoProcessing : 1. Main GUI, (DisplayWidget, buttons, etc.) 
                  2. Extracting frames from video(cv::VideoCapture)
                  3. Frame background substraction(cv::BackgroundSubtractorMOG2)
                 
Preprocess      : 1. void computeMeanAndStd(const QString& filename,int numOfFrames); : compute mean and std of numOfFrames frames of the objective video (calling place : VideoProcessing constructor )
                  2. findBeeHead (calling place : processing for each frame)
                  3. brightnessDistortion : compute shadowMask for shadowRemoval 
                  4. legalRect : exclude BBs (1): totally in beehead, 
                                             (2): not attaching to the beehead  
                  5. shadowRemoval : detect BBs of shadows 


